Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore. Put it inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! I don't care who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This man's no good. Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone... Anyone is fine, so please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Begin the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Stick it inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't stall, just stick it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm losing my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, that's the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your sins will be forgiven this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That woman is a devil that took the shape of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now finish it, of your own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mikagura Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Translation: Tamesuu & akutsu | Timing: PlasticYakuza | Editing: Collectr | Typeset & Encode: ShocWave | QC: Brush
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shrike
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there. What are you ladies doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-san sent us to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks Tokiwa Shougo is involved in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a pleasant sight, but I\Nsuppose you'll want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like she was impaled\Nafter being strangled to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that word "shrike" on her stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no idea at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive someone who'd do something so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we find the culprit quickly,\Nthere will be another victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ladies going to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. I'm working here as a waitress now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So this place has become a normal restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you know what a shrike is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A shrike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about it. I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to have a strong effect on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be a good bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Please let us through!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be. Just when she was doing so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unforgivable. I will find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We already know who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A witness saw a man fleeing from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawaba's heading there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawaba! Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't even put up a fight. It was an easy catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the mimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, his name's Gonzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,People say the shrike is good at mimicry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably wrote that word on the corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as a hint that he was responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw that word, of course\NI immediately knew it was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He confessed, too. He admitted killing two women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,God... told me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been around for several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that I hadn't seen him in\Na while, and I was getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to see Mikagura-sensei now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's smelling salts. There will probably\Nbe opium fumes where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who has no tolerance to opium\Nwill be very susceptible to its effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you start to hallucinate, sniff that,\Nand get out of there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do that! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a very good shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should've stayed with my brother after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I couldn't just leave her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up. It's not like you to get so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late. I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I had to take care of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think Gonzo is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I did some research or him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good at mimicry, but he's not educated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know how to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But "shrike" was written on the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you think that\Nthe culprit is someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He blamed his crime on someone else and\Nis walking around carefree as can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to use bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit will repeat his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone hangs around where he's likely to appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll fall for the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The murderer only targets beautiful women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't fit the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll step forward and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so flat-chested that at night,\Nhe'd mistake you for a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Let's decide the matter fairly by drawing lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No hard feelings for whoever gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she be all right? Maybe I should've gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you that you don't fit the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in moping because of\Nsomething that's already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we have to focus on rescuing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Houran-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Shinbu-san and ask him to\Nhelp us look for Chizuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing is, Shinbu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, my brother, hasn't been around in days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine. Now let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To the place where Gonzo said God\Ntold him to commit his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, this smell is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My body feels... hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san, snap out of it! Don't you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. You've regained your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My body won't stop throbbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave it like this, it'll feel painful for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you touch me right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have more, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Get a hold of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make me feel good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a little giddy, but I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I didn't mean for it to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm glad it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, we have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends will definitely find this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait for them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I promise I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then confess your sins and pray to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one who'll be confessing to his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You used Gonzo to kill your wife, Chizue-san,\Nand Kuramoto Akane-san, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why would you do those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that woman's fault! It's all her fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Shove it into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Do you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that you have any right to\Ncomplain in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even capable of doing\Nwhat makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If it does, you should make that useless\Nthing between your legs work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can do that, I'll take you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But that will never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to kill her, but I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I heard that man's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you can't do it yourself, make someone else do it."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was easy to plant the idea of killing\Nmy wife into that dimwit, Gonzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"That woman is the devil. That's\Nwhy she sleeps with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"But at this rate, you'll be possessed by a devil, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote "shrike" on the corpses to hint that\NGonzo was responsible and cause his arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I impaled her because my desire for\Nrevenge overpowered my love for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But as I was impaling her body,\Nsomething unbelievable happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My useless dick was revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forget that feeling, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You used Gonzo to kill Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't care who it was. It could have been anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaburagi-san, it couldn't have been just anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A man taught you how to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Tokiwa Shougo. Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it looks like a passage that leads\Nto Tokiwa Shougo's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be extremely dangerous from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go anyway, for Akane's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeno-san and Houran,\Nplease stay with Morimatsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-sama, please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought there was\Na cave like this underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiwa Shougo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think we'd meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Give yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it kicking in?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a taste you can easily forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to watch the person you love\Nbeing raped, while being raped yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time to wrap things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... Someone, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san, you're just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.44,0:23:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sold off too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sold? I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:24:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're having the same things\Ndone to you that they did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san, you were sold off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sold...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't keep living like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any choice but to sell Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.92,0:24:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. We have to sell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.11,0:24:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.96,0:24:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to work! If I don't work, they'll sell me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-san, help me! Tokito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless. Nobody will come to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.52,0:24:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it was for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.96,0:24:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one you can depend on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.35,0:24:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to defend yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.48,0:24:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.92,0:24:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill him, everything will turn out fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.52,0:24:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.32,0:24:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm passing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.40,0:24:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a person's been hypnotized, it's easy\Nto make them re-enter a hypnotic state,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.72,0:24:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,although it didn't work last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.04,0:24:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now kill the man in front of you and free yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.60,0:25:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.16,0:25:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,– Get a hold of yourself, Tomoe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.72,0:25:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,– Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.96,0:25:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,– Have some of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.76,0:25:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,– Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.40,0:25:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.88,0:25:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what you were about to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.68,0:25:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's not talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.96,0:25:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over! Give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.20,0:25:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This keeps getting more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.88,0:25:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just finish all of you together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.96,0:25:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.84,0:25:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Mikagura Tokito!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.00,0:25:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.00,0:26:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiwa Shougo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.72,0:26:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, Tokiwa Shougo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.80,0:26:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We've sealed off all of your escape routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.92,0:26:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.60,0:26:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.56,0:26:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikagura Tokito. This was a fun game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.88,0:26:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it... over?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.04,0:27:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now he'll pay for all of his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.60,0:27:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.40,0:27:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.24,0:27:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally going back to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.76,0:27:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Houran, you're coming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.72,0:27:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.96,0:27:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.00,0:27:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, I'm actually Ranmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.44,0:27:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.64,0:27:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How could you say that? Of course I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.35,0:27:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Tokito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.88,0:27:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.48,0:27:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.88,0:27:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Shakuryuu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.96,0:27:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.76,0:27:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.35,0:27:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember you and your\Nfriends for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.16,0:28:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You two seem very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.60,0:28:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.16,0:28:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.44,0:28:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Shigeno-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.28,0:28:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.52,0:28:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.16,0:28:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}anata ni todoke watashi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.16,0:28:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I send my heart to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.16,0:28:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kanashii yoru wa hitori namida ga ko to ko to ko
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.16,0:28:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On a sorrowful night, alone, my tears go drip, drop, drip, drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.12,0:28:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}anata ni todoke watashi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.12,0:28:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I send my heart to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.08,0:29:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}shizukana yoru ni hikaru tobira no oto oto oto oto
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.08,0:29:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,On a quiet night, the sound of a door –\Nthe sound, the sound, the sound, the sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.76,0:29:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.26,0:29:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.48,0:29:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only morning, and you're already so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.68,0:29:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Has your wound healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.28,0:29:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm better than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun, a new job has come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.92,0:29:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.64,0:29:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Tokito-san!